---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Website & App Development Agency"
    bodyclass="inner-page contact-page"
>
    <div class="rts-breadcrumb-area bg_image">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <div class="baread-crumb-main-wrapper pt--100">
                        <div class="inner">
                            <h1 class="title rts_hero__title">
                                Terms & Conditions
                            </h1>
                            <span class="bg-text">Terms & Conditions</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="appoinmnet-area-two rts-section-gap">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <h6>Effective Date: 1/12/2024</h6>
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <p>
                            Welcome to CartPlus (“we,” “our,” “us”), a Shopify
                            app designed to enhance cart management and improve
                            the shopping experience. By installing and using
                            CartPlus, you agree to the following Terms and
                            Conditions. If you do not agree, please uninstall
                            the app and discontinue its use.
                        </p>
                        <h4 class="mb-2">1. Definitions</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                “App” refers to CartPlus, including all
                                associated features, services, and updates.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                “Merchant” refers to any Shopify store owner or
                                authorized user installing and using the app.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                “User” refers to customers of the Merchant’s
                                Shopify store.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                “Service” refers to the functionality provided
                                by the app to improve cart management and
                                related features.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">2. Acceptance of Terms</h4>
                        <p class="mb-0">
                            By installing or using CartPlus, you confirm that:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                You have the authority to bind your Shopify
                                store to these terms.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                You will comply with all applicable laws and
                                regulations.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">3. License</h4>
                        <p class="mb-0">
                            We grant you a non-exclusive, revocable, and
                            non-transferable license to use CartPlus on your
                            Shopify store.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">4. Merchant Responsibilities</h4>
                        <p class="mb-0">Merchants are responsible for:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                Providing accurate information during app setup.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Ensuring compliance with applicable data
                                protection laws for customer data.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Managing the app’s configurations and ensuring
                                its suitability for their store.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">5. Data Collection and Usage</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                CartPlus may collect non-personal and personal
                                data as outlined in our [Privacy Policy].
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Data collected will be used to provide, enhance,
                                and optimize app functionality.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Merchants must obtain consent from their users
                                if required by applicable laws.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">6. Fees and Billing</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                CartPlus offers [free and/or paid plans]. Paid
                                plans are billed through Shopify’s billing
                                system.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Fees are non-refundable except as required by
                                law.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Failure to pay fees may result in suspension or
                                termination of access to the app.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">7. Support and Updates</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                We will provide reasonable support for the app.
                                Support requests can be directed to info@appvertix.com
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                The app may be updated to improve functionality
                                or ensure compatibility with Shopify’s platform.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">8. Intellectual Property</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                CartPlus, including its design, code, and
                                features, is our intellectual property.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Merchants may not copy, modify, or redistribute
                                any part of the app without prior written
                                consent.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">9. Disclaimer of Warranties</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                CartPlus is provided “as is” without warranties
                                of any kind.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                We do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free
                                operation of the app.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Merchants assume all risks associated with using
                                the app.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">10. Limitation of Liability</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                To the fullest extent permitted by law, we are
                                not liable for any indirect, incidental, or
                                consequential damages arising from the use of
                                CartPlus.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Our total liability is limited to the fees paid
                                for the app in the 3 months preceding the claim.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">11. Termination</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                Merchants may uninstall CartPlus at any time.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                We may terminate or suspend access to the app if
                                these terms are violated.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">12. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                These terms are governed by the laws of Ludhiana.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Disputes will be resolved in the courts of
                                Ludhiana.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">13. Changes to Termss</h4>
                        <p class="mb-0">
                            We reserve the right to update these Terms and
                            Conditions. Continued use of the app after updates
                            constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">14. Contact Us</h4>
                        <p class="mb-0">
                            For questions or concerns regarding these Terms and
                            Conditions, please contact us:<br />
                            Email: info@appvertix.com<br />
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
